      .row
        .span5.testimonial
          "It's a little like Wes Anderson meets Gary Vaynerchuck."
          %br
          %small
            %i.pull-right - Benjamin Simons, Alexandria Nicole Cellars
        .offset2.span5.testimonial
          "Your guide to drinking wine, pop culture and the business of the vine. "
          %br
          %small
            %i.pull-right - @WineDiggs

